## How to Promote an Item

**Parking lot -> Post-launch V1.1**: You've hit launch, customers are using v1, and this feature is now the #1 ask. Run `scope_tool.py rescope` to move it up.

**Parking lot -> Launch-blocking**: You've discovered through customer conversations that the MVP can't ship without it. Also requires `rescope` -- AND requires you to remove something else from launch-blocking to make room. No net adds.

**Post-launch V1.1 -> Launch-blocking**: Same trade rule. Something else goes back to parking lot or gets outright dropped.

## How to Retire an Item

Every 90 days, walk the parking lot. Any idea that hasn't felt pulled in 90 days and doesn't excite you anymore -- delete it. A shorter parking lot is a healthier parking lot.

